  "key": "C major",
  "genre": [
    "Ballad",
    "Ambient"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 3,
  "lyrics": "In a spectrum of dreams, are you what you seem? Is it closer than it seems? At the seams it flees. Stitching everywhere, dreams along, and long to stare, Monsters underneath to stare, without calling from the dark. Do you wanna fight with what everyone thinks? I know you're specimen, you're chilling in my specimen, Just a specimen, just a specimen I know inside, So I'm gonna fly, fly, fly, fly, fly, fly, fly, baby, I want you to fly, Just tell me now, tell me where you're going, fly high, And if it does anything, you could possibly imagine you're mine, mine, And if it will, I'll do the same, Got a DNA trip, got a DNA trip, Went over to a parlor, check it, got big, Do I know it, do you show it, Tell the feelings that you're feeling, it all goes down, And we're human, that's how it goes down, Giving it all around, Giving it all around, The spectrum of me, the separateness of you, it's like we're the same, Evading all my thoughts, and all our thoughts, And our time here is different, I can't help, because you, tell yourself, things can't, become of you now, Tell yourself bye, Bye,",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 20.059999465942383,
      "text": "In a spectrum of dreams, are you what you seem?",
      "start": 12.619999885559082
    },
    {
      "end": 24.34000015258789,
      "text": "Is it closer than it seems?",
      "start": 21.5
    },
    {
      "end": 27.780000686645508,
      "text": "At the seams it flees.",
      "start": 25.479999542236328
    },
    {
      "end": 37.959999084472656,
      "text": "Stitching everywhere, dreams along, and long to stare,",
      "start": 33.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 44.959999084472656,
      "text": "Monsters underneath to stare, without calling from the dark.",
      "start": 39.099998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 55.47999954223633,
      "text": "Do you wanna fight with what everyone thinks?",
      "start": 45.7599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 63.060001373291016,
      "text": "I know you're specimen, you're chilling in my specimen,",
      "start": 56.7599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 70.58000183105469,
      "text": "Just a specimen, just a specimen I know inside,",
      "start": 65.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 87.73999786376953,
      "text": "So I'm gonna fly, fly, fly, fly, fly, fly, fly, baby, I want you to fly,",
      "start": 71.54000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 96.18000030517578,
      "text": "Just tell me now, tell me where you're going, fly high,",
      "start": 89.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 109.0199966430664,
      "text": "And if it does anything, you could possibly imagine you're mine, mine,",
      "start": 96.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 143.17999267578125,
      "text": "And if it will, I'll do the same,",
      "start": 139.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 154.05999755859375,
      "text": "Got a DNA trip, got a DNA trip, Went over to a parlor, check it, got big,",
      "start": 145.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 163.44000244140625,
      "text": "Do I know it, do you show it, Tell the feelings that you're feeling, it all goes down,",
      "start": 154.5
    },
    {
      "end": 171.75999450683594,
      "text": "And we're human, that's how it goes down,",
      "start": 166.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 178.74000549316406,
      "text": "Giving it all around,",
      "start": 175.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 186.39999389648438,
      "text": "Giving it all around,",
      "start": 183.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 192.4600067138672,
      "text": "The spectrum of me, the separateness of you, it's like we're the same,",
      "start": 186.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 200.3000030517578,
      "text": "Evading all my thoughts, and all our thoughts, And our time here is different,",
      "start": 193.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 212.5,
      "text": "I can't help, because you, tell yourself, things can't, become of you now,",
      "start": 202.02000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 214.6999969482422,
      "text": "Tell yourself bye,",
      "start": 212.9199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 226.52000427246094,
      "text": "Bye,",
      "start": 225.1199951171875
    }
  ],
